{"tid":848564,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"[召喚admin] discussion thread 「顯示更多」改善芻議","createTime":"2018-10-05T04:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T05:55:03.000Z","uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"44f8ccef5919bd9e65e60ad10376f4454edbade8","tid":848564,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T04:27:38.000Z","msg":"依家用網頁版討論嘅時候<br />\nquote人地段長文 好阻地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要scroll落去好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家好似要3個replies in succession<br />\n先至開始將啲comment縮做「顯示更多」<br />\n例如<br />\n敢言學者Jordan Peterson：大學已經畀危險嘅左翼份子操控<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/BjxRmV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/BjxRmV</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以更新功能<br />\n自動detect 個quoted comment嘅長短，<br />\n如果長過某個限度就縮做「顯示更多」<br />\nexpand咗之後可以選擇「顯示更少」<br />\n即係類似youtube comment咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e34ff2f3c1b114a9a6358ddf158c253f0df5ae2","tid":848564,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T05:02:05.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af0be387074f02e5fafa42f7d03ef1dda64ca189","tid":848564,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T05:55:03.000Z","msg":"即係同通知有人引用你回覆分開一段比你睇?"}]}